text: Demetrious is a given name. Notable people with the given name include: *Demetrious Cox (born 1994), American football player *Demetrious Johnson (born 1986), American mixed martial artist *Demetrious Johnson (born 1961), American football player *Demetrious Maxie (born 1973), Canadian football player *Demetrious Nicholson (born 1992), American football player ==See also== *Demetrious, character from Dragon Ball Z: Bardock – The Father of Goku
